---
title: Moroccan Honey Pork & Garlic Rice Bowl with Dill-Parsley Yoghurt & Cucumber Salsa
description: This meal is all about the little differences – the ras el hanout spicing up the pork, the flavourful garlic rice flecked with cucumber salsa and the dill-parsley yoghurt drizzle that will become your new favourite accompaniment.
